title: Couple With Heart Man Medium Skin Tone Woman Medium Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic couple, specifically a woman with medium skin tone and a man with medium skin tone, united by a heart symbol. It signifies love, partnership, and affection between two people.
apple_vendor_description: This depiction of a couple on Apple devices showcases a man and woman, both with medium skin tones, connected by a vibrant red heart. Apple's characteristic glossy 3D shading gives the heart a luminous quality, while the figures are drawn with smooth gradients and gentle outlines. The emoji beautifully symbolizes love, partnership, and deep affection, radiating a warm and joyful connection.
